{"tid":850213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一旦開戰你願為祖國捐多少？","createTime":"2018-10-06T09:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T10:35:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":333,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"42fd346f4456f02f2fcbc688e83265181d4fc24c","tid":850213,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"隨著中美貿易戰不斷升級，大陸門戶網站網易旗下一個軍事欄目推出影片節目，詢問「一旦爆發戰爭 你願意為祖國捐出多少積蓄？」<br />\n<br />\n這個影片本是指責美國，但稱每次戰爭後美國經濟不但沒有崩潰，反而愈戰愈勇，原因是「每次作戰美國老百姓都積極捐款捐資產」，甚至女子也積極參軍，而戰後國家又會給老兵很好的福利，確保一輩子衣食無憂。<br />\n<br />\n影片中問道，中共雖然製造出了航母、東風......但問題是中國龐大的人口數量，到底會成為動力還是影響國家決策的壓力呢？因為航母一旦開動，就不是幾百億的事，到時候財政入不敷出，國人是否會像美國那樣捐錢捐資產呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/i-epochtimes-com/assets-uploads-2018-08-DkVMEC9XgAEOwS_-600x477@1200x1200.jpg?url=http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/08/DkVMEC9XgAEOwS_-600x477.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2Fi-epochtimes-com%2Fassets-uploads-2018-08-DkVMEC9XgAEOwS_-600x477%401200x1200.jpg%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2FDkVMEC9XgAEOwS_-600x477.jpg&h=d2b95c0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘管該影片給出的答案是「肯定」的，並舉例抗日戰爭時國人捐款捐物，但此時非彼時。頻頻遭受毒奶粉、毒疫苗、紅藍黃毒害，又頻頻遭遇股市圈錢、融資平台詐騙、P2P平台詐騙的國人們早已清醒了。後面大量網民的跟帖則給出了另一個非常不同的答案。目前大量跟帖已經被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/i-epochtimes-com/assets-uploads-2018-08-Dkd-mic-gAAQsiK@1200x1200.jpg-large-600x400?url=http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/08/DkdxmicXgAAQsiK.jpg-large-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2Fi-epochtimes-com%2Fassets-uploads-2018-08-Dkd-mic-gAAQsiK%401200x1200.jpg-large-600x400%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2FDkdxmicXgAAQsiK.jpg-large-600x400.jpg&h=7440c6bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/i-epochtimes-com/assets-uploads-2018-08-1-82-600x536@1200x1200.jpg?url=http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/08/1-82-600x536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2Fi-epochtimes-com%2Fassets-uploads-2018-08-1-82-600x536%401200x1200.jpg%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F1-82-600x536.jpg&h=33f2c980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/i-epochtimes-com/assets-uploads-2018-08-2-36-600x528@1200x1200.jpg?url=http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/08/2-36-600x528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2Fi-epochtimes-com%2Fassets-uploads-2018-08-2-36-600x528%401200x1200.jpg%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F2-36-600x528.jpg&h=43dc7b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/i-epochtimes-com/assets-uploads-2018-08-3-25-600x720@1200x1200.jpg?url=http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/08/3-25-600x720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2Fi-epochtimes-com%2Fassets-uploads-2018-08-3-25-600x720%401200x1200.jpg%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F3-25-600x720.jpg&h=f3d456c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/i-epochtimes-com/assets-uploads-2018-08-juan-600x1111@1200x1200.jpg?url=http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/08/juan-600x1111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2Fi-epochtimes-com%2Fassets-uploads-2018-08-juan-600x1111%401200x1200.jpg%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Fjuan-600x1111.jpg&h=b66fda42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2018-08-14/83112188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2018-08-14%2F83112188&d=Lh5EBkH1FGt7o%2BWrmTGuSZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=678f28a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2018-08-14/83112188</a>"},{"pid":"b02c28e6f8d65d5f9ee606b922be958abaee2e7d","tid":850213,"uid":89509,"like":381,"dislike":2,"score":379,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"毅進星 100（美國）"},{"pid":"0a489037b4b813bf85b06b67a7fbdef4ad1e245a","tid":850213,"uid":136662,"like":245,"dislike":1,"score":244,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:00:13.000Z","msg":"又有一班誠實人俾人查水錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b332b6b8aecfe2e9be40488a39ea80dfce365af","tid":850213,"uid":89868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7885a810526cb56ccb2a4d5ce2f551dbb2b61086","tid":850213,"uid":19978,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:03:13.000Z","msg":"民不聊生未天怒人怨囉<br />\n<br />\n國泰民安未一堆順民囉"},{"pid":"2f12b9ec1495476dee6884629a91dfa94e631267","tid":850213,"uid":39575,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:03:44.000Z","msg":"捐精得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ad730e84d5a07cca3c929afb1a0cc0225fa7f4","tid":850213,"uid":144718,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"美軍來了<br />\n我來帶路"},{"pid":"423d48e1b831ec2c8475f4b7d2e3befd58b0f375","tid":850213,"uid":8105,"like":196,"dislike":1,"score":195,"quote":{"pid":"64ad730e84d5a07cca3c929afb1a0cc0225fa7f4","tid":850213,"uid":144718,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"美軍來了<br />\n我來帶路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/06/180858_72e9a9ef19ff704e6521c18112f42050.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F06%2F180858_72e9a9ef19ff704e6521c18112f42050.png&h=